summary: Inktober 2018 Day Twenty Two: “Nothing Too Expensive This Time, OK Guys?”  “THIS IS ALL I EVER SING!  THIS IS MY...
caption:
Inktober 2018 Day Twenty Two: “Nothing Too Expensive This Time, OK Guys?”

 “THIS IS ALL I EVER SING!  THIS IS MY SOOOOOOOOOUL!!!”

So I think my single overall favorite element of “Aggretsuko” isn’t simply its cast but rather the layers of relationships that form between them; the specifics of their friendships feel so real and so compelling, especially because at the center of it all is this genuine affection and protectiveness toward each other, which is ultimately what I wanted to reflect here (especially because my BIG hope for Season 2 is that we get to see Retusko’s two groups of friends interact on that level).
